These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, photographer, firefighter
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, volleyball, snowboarding
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, traveling, writing
House: palace, townhouse, wooden
City: berlin, colone, prague
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, tram
 1. the palace house is not the person who's hobby is traveling##6
 2. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the wooden house##5
 4. the person traveling to prague is somewhere between the musician and the person driving the tram##7
 5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the wooden house##1
 6. the photographer is the person driving the bike##1
 7. the person who's hobby is writing is not the person traveling to colone##6
 8. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 9. the townhouse house is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
10. the person driving the tram is not the person who's hobby is writing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3     |
| Job      | musician       | photographer  | firefighter     |
| Sport          | snowboarding       | volleyball  | parkour    |
| Hobby         | card-games  | writing   | traveling |
| House   | palace | wooden   | townhouse     |
| City   | berlin  | prague | colone   |
| Transport           | jet-ski  | bike      | tram  |

