House: craftsman, art-deco, cape-cod
 1. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 2. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the left of the art-deco house##5
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is in the middle##1
 4. the person playing backgammon is somewhere between the game-smoker and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
 5. the person who's hobby is hiking is not the craftsman house##6
 6. the person drinking juice is between the person traveling to boston and the person playing domino##2
 7. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is board-games##7
 9. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1
10. the game-smoker is not the person traveling to boston##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2        |      3       |
| Beverage          | iced-tea       | juice         | hot-chocolate         |
