.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, sprite
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, lacrosse, volleyball
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, colombian, spanish
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, ritmeester, tiparillo
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, white, aquamarine
3 different games are played: bridge, whist, canasta
 1. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
 2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 3. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who likes white##1
 4. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere between the tiparillo-smoker and the bolivar-smoker##7
 5. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
 6. the colombian is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
 7. the brazilian is between the person drinking cola and the person who likes aquamarine##2
 8. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
 9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is swimming is not the colombian##6
11. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the brazilian##1
12. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | cola      | hot-chocolate | sprite      |
| Sport          | lacrosse    | swimming          | volleyball |
| Nationality           | colombian   | brazilian    | spanish    |
| Cigar   | bolivar | ritmeester       | tiparillo      |
| Color   | purple   | white           | aquamarine      |
| Game           | canasta     | bridge           | whist  |

