.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, cola, hot-chocolate
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, fonseca, dannemann
House: ranch-style, tower, gothic-revival
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, december, august
City: edinburgh, colone, hamburg
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, trike
 1. the person drinking juice is not the person traveling to edinburgh##6
 2. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in august##7
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the dannemann-smoker##1
 5. the person traveling to edinburgh is the dannemann-smoker##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
 7. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the ranch-style house is the person driving the trike##1
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the right of the gothic-revival house##5
10. the person who's birthday is in october is the fonseca-smoker##1
11. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage           | hot-chocolate    | juice | cola    |
| Cigar   | dannemann       | fonseca    | baccarat   |
| House   | gothic-revival        | tower  | ranch-style |
| Birthday           | august       | october   | december     |
| City         | edinburgh | hamburg | colone |
| Transport     | roller       | helicopter | trike    |

 